ENOUGH REVENGE YET?

294
00:18:56,875 --> 00:18:59,125
- NO, NOT UNTIL YOU'RE DEAD.

295
00:19:05,708 --> 00:19:07,833
- COME ON.
THIS HAS GONE WAY TOO FAR.

296
00:19:07,916 --> 00:19:09,166
